SpendWise is a full-stack personal finance tracker where users can register, 
log in, and manage their income and expenses. 
The frontend is built with React and communicates with a Node.js/Express backend using Axios. 
Authentication is handled using JWT, 
and passwords are securely hashed using bcrypt before being stored in MongoDB.
 Each transaction is linked to the logged-in user, 
so users can only access their own financial data. 
The app supports adding, editing, deleting, filtering transactions, 
and calculating income, expenses, and balance.